Package: TemporalConsistency
Type: Package
Title: Computes Traditional and New Estimates of Temporal Consistency Per DeSimone(2015)
Version: 0.1.2
Author: James M. LeBreton <jlebreto@gmail.com>
Maintainer: James M. LeBreton <jlebreto@gmail.com>
Description: This package includes functions to compute a number of estimates of temporal consistency 
    recommended by DeSimone(2015) including: a) component loadings for temporal consistency (cl_tc), 
    test-retest correlations (cor_tc), c) square root mean residual using T1 and T2 item-level
    correlations, and d) person-level temporal consistency estimating using D^2 (d_ptc). All of the 
    statistics may be requested using the tc_all function. 
Depends: R (>= 4.5) 
Imports: psych (>= 2.5.3),
         stats (>= 4.5.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
